grate sound quality .... this show smokes , hands down ...a 15 minute sugaree ... set closing dancin' a sizzling scarlet ~>fire ... i am rolling thru the space ~>other one right now... i love these early 79 shows ...  from jan to may ...every one .... but thats not why i am here ... 
i just wanted to say i am really enjoying these joani walker tapes ... .this sounds awesome ....
i am going thru the auds right now and grabbing all of them i can find ....and packing them away on the old hd.  
thank you joani and charlie ... 
i will go all the way for this one ....5 for sound quality ....5 for content ... so  .... 5. 
:)

nice 79 show hey people this is a nice dl-sound quality is good(b+)and the band is on!!! to all you sbd lovas i think auds add a more intimate feel!!and this dl really captures that feeling of "being there" turn it up!woo-hoo!!!

Were you there? Post-show, a police car was parked directly in front of the Civic Center and somebody artfully poured chartreuse colored day-glo paint over the blue stobe light on the roof. The paint was seeping down onto the white roof and the reflections of the streetlights off the bleeding colors was inspirational, so a group of anywhere from 10-15 people (it has been 30 years and you know how we tend to exaggarate in our old age)gathered around the car and somebody had a camera and took the picture. If you can share anything about this event I would love to know if you can track down that picture!! For this reason it gets five stars! Audience participation. Email me at: matthew.fleisig@pacer.com Peace
First dead show This is the first dead show I attended.  They did a lot of songs in which I had some emotional investment, particularly "scarlet begonias"
bread crumb Brent officially arrives 11 minutes into Sugaree.  No further questions.

To Joani Walker & Paul Scotton Not the first time I've seen your names. Thank you for recording the shows you attended & doing such a good job of it & for making them available so all of this could be possible. Not sure if you will ever notice this but if you do please know that you are very much appreciated!! And if you happen to know them please direct their attention here please. Thanks & lots of love to all!!
